sets.title: Intensive chest
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 10

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
Drop sets and challenging tempos will test your control, so lock your technique down with the tutorials before firing up your chest.

The challenge isn't over until you've smashed the fiery core finisher!

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your body ready for a strong workout.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: Put in big reps, then push to failure with the drop set.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Switch incline to hit your pecs from every angle.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Follow the specified tempo for the push-ups to increase time under tension.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Take those pectoral muscles as far as they can go.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Fast reps will build the burn in your abs.
